Text: COMP373 - Week 3 - 14/9 to 20/9.September 20, 2020.  .
14/9Met with the team before the client meeting today.
Went over where we were at with the project so far.
The meeting with the client was productive and positive, however, they keep asking for more things and adding previously unknown variables into the mix.
I asked them to come back to us with a priority list so we can focus our efforts in the right area.

Started working on the UI to improve it and add the features requested by the client.

need to add the control and responsiveness next.

Hopeful one of the others may be able to see what I am missing when we meet tomorrow.
11/9Met with the team today before Signal meeting.
Made a lot of progress.
Now have the MVVM structure working and the skeleton of the control and loading of data is ready to go once the database is connected.
18/9 + 19/9Weekend off for anniversary.
Summary.
